Irish Gaelic name <i>Béibhinn</i> ‘white lady’, pronounced ‘bee-<b>veen</b>’). The actress  Vivien Leigh  (  1913–67 ) was christened <i>Vivian</i>."]},{"name":"Vivian","meanings":["Originally a boy's name, from an Old French form of the Latin name <i>Vivianus</i> (probably a derivative of <i>vivus</i> ‘alive’), but now more frequent as a girl's name. The name was borne by a 5th-century bishop of Saintes in western France, remembered for protecting his people during the invasion of the Visigoths."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"When Diepold VII von Vohburg Hohenburg was born about 1179, his father, Berthold II von Vohburg Markgraf, was 51 and his mother, Adelheid von Ballenstedt, was 22. He married Mathilde Von Wasserburg before 1211, in Oberbayern, Bavaria, Germany. They were the parents of at least 1 daughter. He died on 26 December 1226, at the age of 48."},"et":{"UM 1179–26 DEZ 1226":"umbes 1179–26. detsember 1226","1179–1226":"1179–1226","1189–1237":"1189–1237","1211–1266":"1211–1266","1130–1181":"1130–1181","1157–1183":"1157–1183","before 1211":"enne 1211","ABT 15 SEP 1181":"umbes 22. september 1181","26 DEZ 1226":"26. detsember 1226","1130":"1130","1183":"1183","1181":"1181","1226":"1226","1237":"1237","Abt 1211":"umbes 1211","1157":"1157","1179":"1179","1266":"1266","1211":"1211","1189":"1189","UM 1179":"umbes 1179","Aft. 1183":"pärast 1183","Oberbayern, Bavaria, Germany":"Oberbayern, Bayern, Saksamaa","Vohburg, Oberbayern, Bavaria, Germany":"Vohburg an der Donau, Landkreis Pfaffenhofen an der Ilm, Bayern, Saksamaa"},"fi":{"UM 1179–26 DEZ 1226":"noin 1179–26. joulukuuta 1226","1179–1226":"1179–1226","1189–1237":"1189–1237","1211–1266":"1211–1266","1130–1181":"1130–1181","1157–1183":"1157–1183","before 1211":"ennen vuotta 1211","ABT 15 SEP 1181":"noin 22. syyskuuta 1181","26 DEZ 1226":"26. joulukuuta 1226","1130":"1130","1183":"1183","1181":"1181","1226":"1226","1237":"1237","Abt 1211":"noin 1211","1157":"1157","1179":"1179","1266":"1266","1211":"1211","1189":"1189","UM